citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
**A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:30 a.m.
on 03/25/2016. The inspector called the contact number listed, however, the number was disconnected. The
inspector knocked on the front door but there was no answer.
